\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":20978,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2015\/10\/03\/ali-nasihah-believers-good-will\/","url_meta":{"origin":25363,"position":3},"title":"Ali on Sincerity: Believers have good will, love for each other","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 3, 2015","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn 'Asakir reported: Ali ibn Abi Talib, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cVerily, the believers are people with good will and love for each other, even if their lands and countries are far apart. The hypocrites are people with malevolence for each other.\u201d Source: Ta\u0304ri\u0304kh Dimashq 23310 \u0639\u0646\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":39249,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/03\/17\/prophet-never-intercedes\/","url_meta":{"origin":25363,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Oppression: The Prophet never intercedes for tyrants or renegades","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 17, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Umamah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cTwo kinds of people from my nation will never receive my intercession: an oppressive and malevolent leader, and every extremist renegade.\u201d Source: al-Mu\u2019jam al-Kabi\u0304r lil-T\u0323abara\u0304ni\u0304 8079 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e